    #currently do nothing... replace was done elsewhere (string operations)

df_1['LU-Wechsel'] = ['\n'.join(wrap(x, 80)) for x in  df_1['LU-Wechsel']]
df_1['LU-Wechsel'] = df_1['LU-Wechsel'].str.replace('outer', 'Restklasse', regex=True)
df_1['LU-Wechsel'] = df_1['LU-Wechsel'].str.replace('Sonstige Sport, Freizeit, Erholung', '', regex=True)
df_1['LU-Wechsel'] = df_1['LU-Wechsel'].str.replace(':', '', regex=True)

ax = df_1.plot(kind='barh', 
               color='C0', 
               figsize=(5,18), 
               title='Barrierenwahrscheinlichkeit nach LU-Wechsel', 
               zorder=3,
               label=df_1['LU-Wechsel'])
ax.xaxis.grid(True, zorder=0)
ax.set_yticklabels(remove_long_captures(df_1['LU-Wechsel']))
plt.xlabel("p", labelpad=14)
